HEADWORD: Inartificial
<hw>In*ar`ti*fi"cial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>artificial</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>inartificiel</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not artificial; not made or
elaborated by art; natural; simple; artless; <as>as, an
<ex>inartificial</ex> argument; an <ex>inartificial</ex>
character.</as></def> -- <wordforms><wf>In*ar`ti*fi"cial*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>In*ar`ti*fi"cial*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
